the week's news; an author's
inspiration from

10:17.116 --> 10:31.865 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Norse mythology; and much more.

10:31.898 --> 10:36.769 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Secretary of State Rex Tillerson
at one of
