snapping
pictures.

11:31.424 --> 11:34.661 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The secretary arrived at a time
of mounting
tensions.

11:34.694 --> 11:40.466 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
North Korea has test-fired
ballistic missiles
twice in the last three weeks,
as U.S. and

11:40.500 --> 11:44.404 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
South Korean troops conduct
elaborate, annual
joint exercises.

11:44.437 --> 11:48.541 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The North also carried out two
nuclear tests
last year.

11:48.575 --> 11:53.313 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
