of those
perspectives.

19:36.976 --> 19:41.781 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: In 2010, the
American Medical
Association, the largest
physicians group

19:41.814 --> 19:45.551 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
