29:06.878 --> 29:08.847 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: David, what about
the budget
proposal?

29:08.880 --> 29:13.218 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
DAVID BROOKS: Yes, just some
