29:50.589 --> 29:54.526 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Then there's periods of
disruption, where
they are internally divided.

29:54.559 --> 29:56.762 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And the argument is, Jimmy
Carter was an example
was this.

29:56.795 --> 29:59.197 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The Democrats had shifted away
from some old-style
liberalism.

29:59.231 --> 30:01.033 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
