Clinton's style.

30:01.066 --> 30:04.770 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And they were internally
divided, and that
Donald Trump is like Jimmy
Carter.

30:04.803 --> 30:09.174 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
