Republican Party
does not know what it wants, and
that he himself

30:09.207 --> 30:10.942 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
is internally divided.

30:10.976 --> 30:13.945 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And you get these weird
contradictions of
campaigning one way, and then
governing in

30:13.979 --> 30:15.781 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
