the same thing, then, Mark,
about the budget.

30:18.650 --> 30:19.818 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
MARK SHIELDS: I hope not.

30:19.851 --> 30:20.786 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Well, I hope not.

30:20.819 --> 30:21.787 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

30:21.820 --> 30:22.788 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MARK SHIELDS: There's no point
in watching.

30:22.821 --> 30:23.789 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: At least on this
