doing, they are
investing in everything that is
hard power.

31:41.900 --> 31:45.670 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
They're investing in the
military, in homeland
security, everything that is
about threat

31:45.704 --> 31:47.506 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
and fear.

31:47.539 --> 31:52.410 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And they are disinvesting in
everything that
has to do with compassion, with
care, thinking,

31:52.444 --> 31:53.411 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
innovation.

31:53.445 --> 31:55.313 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And it's almost like emotionally
consistent.

31:55.347 --> 31:58.183 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It's just hardness and toughness
and fear.

31:58.216 --> 32:00.018 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
