evidence?

32:42.627 --> 32:44.329 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
MARK SHIELDS: It is universal.

32:44.362 --> 32:48.767 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
When you let -- when lose Devin
Nunes, who
is the chairman of the House
Intelligence

32:48.800 --> 32:49.768 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Committee...

32:49.801 --> 32:51.570 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Republican.

32:51.603 --> 32:54.339 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARK SHIELDS: Republican, who
has been Donald
Trump's apologist, I mean,
explained that

32:54.372 --> 32:59.444 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
