of the United
States.

33:20.732 --> 33:22.367 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
He accused the president of the
United States.

33:22.400 --> 33:25.303 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He said it was a fact that the
president of
the United States had done this.

33:25.337 --> 33:26.338 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
It was wrong.

33:26.371 --> 33:27.505 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
It was unfounded.

33:27.539 --> 33:28.506 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
