34:01.339 --> 34:02.374 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: How do you
explain it?

34:02.407 --> 34:04.109 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
DAVID BROOKS: Yes, there's some
fear.

34:04.142 --> 34:06.278 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
