attention.

34:33.772 --> 34:35.273 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Figuratively
speaking.

34:35.307 --> 34:36.808 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
DAVID BROOKS: Yes, right.

34:36.841 --> 34:37.809 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Right, exactly.

34:37.842 --> 34:41.413 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And the second is that force.

34:41.446 --> 34:42.414 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
