35:05.003 --> 35:09.374 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
And it was a perfectly
legitimate step back,
but it was a partial withdrawal.

35:09.407 --> 35:11.676 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And Trump is always forward,
forward, forward.

35:11.710 --> 35:15.413 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And no sign of
any change on
that one.

