38:29.040 --> 38:30.608 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: So, you had some
fun with this?

38:30.642 --> 38:31.609 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
NEIL GAIMAN: I had a lot of fun
