gods are with us in...

38:46.724 --> 38:50.195 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
NEIL GAIMAN: I feel like the
gods are ours.

38:50.228 --> 38:52.130 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And we are allowed -- we created
them.

38:52.163 --> 38:57.635 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Human beings get to create gods,
and human
beings get to tell stories with
gods.

38:57.669 --> 38:59.737 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
We carry our cultures around
with us.

38:59.771 --> 39:01.673 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
