45:27.959 --> 45:31.395 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
History is full of men and women
who successfully
championed justice and equal
rights.

45:31.429 --> 45:33.531 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Empathy and equality are
powerful stories.

45:33.564 --> 45:35.366 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
They need equally powerful
storytellers.

